ext">2.3 HTTP连接</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#2-3-1-%E9%9D%9E%E6%8C%81%E4%B9%85HTTP"><span class="nav-number">3.3.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">2.3.1 非持久HTTP</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#2-3-2-%E6%8C%81%E4%B9%85HTTP"><span class="nav-number">3.3.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">2.3.2 持久HTTP</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#2-3-3-%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B"><span class="nav-number">3.3.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">2.3.3 响应时间模型</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#2-4-HTTP%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%E6%8A%A5%E6%96%87"><span class="nav-number">3.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">2.4 HTTP请求报文</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#2-5-HTTP%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E6%8A%A5%E6%96%87"><span class="nav-number">3.5.</span> <span class="nav-text">2.5 HTTP响应报文</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#2-6-%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7-%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81-Cookies"><span class="nav-number">3.6.</span> <span class="nav-text">2.6 用户-服务器状态: Cookies</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#2-7-Web%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98-%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8"><span class="nav-number">3.7.</span> <span class="nav-text">2.7 Web缓存(代理服务器)</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#2-7-1-%E4%BE%8B%E5%AD%90"><span class="nav-number">3.7.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">2.7.1 例子</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#2-8-%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6GET"><span class="nav-number">3.8.</span> <span class="nav-text">2.8 条件GET</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-1"><a class="nav-link" href="#3-FTP-%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%BC%A0%E8%BE%93%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE"><span class="nav-number">4.</span> <span class="nav-text">3. FTP: 文件传输协议</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#3-1-%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E4%B8%8E%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E5%88%86%E5%BC%80"><span class="nav-number">4.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">3.1 控制连接与数据连接分开</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#3-2-FTP-%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E3%80%81%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94"><span class="nav-number">4.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">3.2 FTP 命令、响应</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-1"><a class="nav-link" href="#4-Email"><span class="nav-number">5.</span> <span class="nav-text">4. Email</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#4-1-Email%EF%BC%9ASMTP"><span class="nav-number">5.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">4.1 Email：SMTP</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#4-2-%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6%E6%8A%A5%E6%96%87%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F"><span class="nav-number">5.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">4.2 邮件报文格式</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#4-3-%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE"><span class="nav-number">5.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">4.3 邮件访问协议</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-1"><a class="nav-link" href="#5-DNS"><span class="nav-number">6.</span> <span class="nav-text">5. DNS</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#5-1-%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D-%E5%88%86%E5%B1%82%E5%BC%8F"><span class="nav-number">6.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">5.1 如何进行设备命名(分层式)</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#5-1-1-DNS%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2"><span class="nav-number">6.1.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">5.1.1 DNS历史</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#5-1-2-DNS%E6%80%BB%E4%BD%93%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87"><span class="nav-number">6.1.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">5.1.2 DNS总体思想目标</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#5-1-3-DNS%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4"><span class="nav-number">6.1.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">5.1.3 DNS命名空间</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#5-2-%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98-%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8"><span class="nav-number">6.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">5.2 解析问题-名字服务器</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#5-2-1-%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95"><span class="nav-number">6.2.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">5.2.1 区域名字服务器维护资源记录</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#5-2-3-DNS%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%B4%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B"><span class="nav-number">6.2.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">5.2.3 DNS大致工作过程</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#5-2-4-%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8-local-name-server"><span class="nav-number">6.2.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">5.2.4 本地名字服务器(local name server)</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#5-2-5-DNS%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%E3%80%81%E6%8A%A5%E6%96%87"><span class="nav-number">6.2.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">5.2.5 DNS协议、报文</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#5-3-%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%9F%9F"><span class="nav-number">6.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">5.3 维护问题，新增一个域</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#5-4-%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BBDNS"><span class="nav-number">6.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">5.4 攻击DNS</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-1"><a class="nav-link" href="#6-P2P%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8"><span class="nav-number">7.</span> <span class="nav-text">6. P2P应用</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#6-1-%E7%BA%AFP2P%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84"><span class="nav-number">7.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">6.1 纯P2P架构</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#6-2-%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%86%E5%8F%91"><span class="nav-number">7.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">6.2 文件分发</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#6-3-%E9%9D%9E%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%8C%96P2P"><span class="nav-number">7.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">6.3 非结构化P2P</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#6-3-1-%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E5%8C%96%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95-BitTorrent"><span class="nav-number">7.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">6.3.1  集中化目录 BitTorrent</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#6-3-2-%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E5%88%86%E5%B8%83%E5%BC%8F-Gnutella"><span class="nav-number">7.5.</span> <span class="nav-text">6.3.2 完全分布式 Gnutella</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-1"><a class="nav-link" href="#7-CDN%E5%92%8C%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E6%B5%81%E5%8C%96%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1"><span class="nav-number">8.</span> <span class="nav-text">7. CDN和视频流化服务</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#7-1-%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D"><span class="nav-number">8.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">7.1 视频介绍</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#7-2-%E6%B5%81%E5%8C%96%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1"><span class="nav-number">8.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">7.2 流化服务</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#7-3-content-distribution-networks"><span class="nav-number">8.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">7.3 content distribution networks</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-1"><a class="nav-link" href="#8-TCP-Socket%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B"><span class="nav-number">9.</span> <span class="nav-text">8. TCP Socket编程</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-1"><a class="nav-link" href="#9-UDPsocket%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B"><span class="nav-number">10.</span> <span class="nav-text">9. UDPsocket编程</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-1"><a class="nav-link" href="#10-%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%93"><span class="nav-number">11.</span> <span class="nav-text">10. 小结</span></a></li></ol></div>
        </div>
